HEADWORD: mail slot
<hw>mail slot</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>A usually horizontal slot in a
door through which mail can be delivered. It often has a hinged cover to
keep the opening cloised when not in use.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

